metadata.title: Eurocopter AS350 Écureuil
aws::graph::propositions: Aftermarket Conversions of Eurocopter AS350 Écureuil
Soloy SD1 is an aftermarket conversion of the Eurocopter AS350 Écureuil.
Soloy Super D is an aftermarket conversion of the Eurocopter AS350 Écureuil.
Soloy SD1 is a conversion of the AS350 BA model.
Soloy Super D is a conversion of the AS350 D model.
Soloy SD1 is powered by an LTS101-600A-3A engine.
Soloy Super D is powered by an LTS101-600A-3A engine.
Soloy AllStar is an aftermarket conversion of the Eurocopter AS350 Écureuil.
Soloy AllStar is a conversion of the AS350 BA model.
Soloy AllStar is powered by a Rolls-Royce 250-C30 engine.
Soloy SD2 is an aftermarket conversion of the Eurocopter AS350 Écureuil.
Soloy SD2 is a conversion of the AS350 B2 model.
Soloy SD2 is powered by an LTS101-700D-2 engine.
Heli-Lynx 350FX1 is an aftermarket conversion of the Eurocopter AS350 Écureuil.
Heli-Lynx 350FX1 is a conversion of the AS350 BA model.
Heli-Lynx 350FX1 is powered by an LTS101-600A-3A engine.
Heli-Lynx 350FX2 is an aftermarket conversion of the Eurocopter AS350 Écureuil.
Heli-Lynx 350FX2 is a conversion of the AS350 BA model or AS350 B2 model.
Heli-Lynx 350FX2 is powered by an LTS101-700D-2 engine.
Otech AS350BA+ is an aftermarket conversion of the Eurocopter AS350 Écureuil.
Otech AS350BA+ is a conversion of the AS350 BA model.
Otech AS350BA+ is powered by an LTS101-600A-3A engine.

text:
### Aftermarket conversions
Soloy SD1, Super D
AS350 BA, D powered by an LTS101-600A-3A engine.
Soloy AllStar
AS350 BA powered by a Rolls-Royce 250-C30 engine.
Soloy SD2
AS350 B2 powered by an LTS101-700D-2 engine.

Heli-Lynx 350FX1
AS350 BA powered by an LTS101-600A-3A engine.
Heli-Lynx 350FX2
AS350 BA or AS350 B2 powered by an LTS101-700D-2 engine.
Otech AS350BA+
AS350 BA powered by an LTS101-600A-3A engine.
